data.name: ClientSiteStatusNotes.Text
data.value: Deleting a status may cause synchronisation problems if the status was recently in use as it may still be in use on an activiser client system

data.name: JobStatusNotes.Text
data.value: 1) Job Status codes may not be added nor removed. 2) You may change the descriptions, but this will have no effect on how they are used by activiser.

data.name: RequestStatusNotes.Text
data.value: 1) A status marked as 'Is Client Status' causes requests with that status to be downloaded to client systems. 2) A status marked as 'Is Client Menu Item' can be set by a client system. 3) Status codes may not be deleted using this console, due to the risk of client corruption.
